## `getElem?_extract_of_lt`

Different hypothesis forms: Array uses `k < min j as.size - i`, List uses `i + k < j`.
Array returns `some (as[i + k]'...)`, List returns `as[i + k]?`.

``` lean src/Init/Data/Array/Extract.lean:202-206
